        {
          "type": "frame",
          "id": "IqMmK",
          "name": "Content Area",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "fill": "#131313",
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "sBGfN",
              "name": "Text Column",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "layout": "vertical",
              "gap": 32,
              "padding": [
                48,
                80
              ],
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "m2Y9G",
                  "name": "Paragraph 1",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "gap": 16,
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "datGk",
                      "name": "p1num",
                      "opacity": 0.5,
                      "fill": "#8E9099",
                      "content": "1",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 12,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "HaIJb",
                      "name": "p1text",
                      "fill": "#e5e2e1",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "Let us bow our heads now for prayer. Our heavenly Father, we thank Thee tonight for this, another opportunity to come to worship You. We are thankful to be alive and to have this great revelation of eternal life dwelling within us.\nAnd we've come tonight, Father, to study thy Word together, these great hidden mysteries that's been hid since the foundation of the world. And the Lamb is the only one that can reveal it to us. I pray that He will come among us tonight, and will take of his Word and reveal it to us, that we might know how to be better servants to Him in this end-time. O God, as we see that we are now in the end-time, help us to know our place, Lord, and our frail beings, and the certainty of the coming of the Lord soon. We ask it in Jesus' name. Amen.\nI believe it was David said, \"I was happy when they said unto me, let us go into the house of the Lord.\" It's always a great privilege to come, and the studying of the Word together gives us this great hope.",
                      "lineHeight": 1.8,
                      "fontFamily": "Noto Serif",
                      "fontSize": 16,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "nNqoL",
                  "name": "Paragraph 2",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "gap": 16,
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "9mplB",
                      "name": "p2num",
                      "opacity": 0.5,
                      "fill": "#8E9099",
                      "content": "2",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 12,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "Rdgku",
                      "name": "p2text",
                      "fill": "#e5e2e1",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "Now there's many standing, and I'm just going to hurry as quick as possible. But I trust that you have enjoyed the presence of the Holy Spirit like I have in these last couple of times. And today, I had something to happen that I haven't had for a long time. I was studying on this revelation here, on the opening of the seal.\nYears ago I run through it here-about some twenty years ago I guess, or something like that-but somehow or another I never was just exactly satisfied. It seemed like there was some things… especially in these seals, because those seals are the entire book. It's the book. The whole book is one book sealed. It starts…",
                      "lineHeight": 1.8,
                      "fontFamily": "Noto Serif",
                      "fontSize": 16,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "LA3c7",
                  "name": "Paragraph 3 - Highlighted",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "gap": 16,
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "rmyPB",
                      "name": "p3num",
                      "opacity": 0.5,
                      "fill": "#8E9099",
                      "content": "3",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 12,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "frame",
                      "id": "HWYVa",
                      "name": "P3 Body",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "layout": "vertical",
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "frame",
                          "id": "UeVrJ",
                          "name": "Yellow Highlight",
                          "fill": "#facc1525",
                          "cornerRadius": 2,
                          "padding": [
                            2,
                            4
                          ],
                          "children": [
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "id": "JSYr3",
                              "name": "p3hlText",
                              "fill": "#e5e2e1",
                              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                              "width": 900,
                              "content": "For instance, if I had something here… I'd show you what I mean. Here is one Seal. That's one… And you roll it up like this-the way it was rolled. And you roll it up in this manner, and at the end there is a little piece sticking out like that. That's the first seal. All right. Then that's the first part of the book. Then the next seal is rolled in this manner, right by the side of it.",
                              "lineHeight": 1.8,
                              "fontFamily": "Noto Serif",
                              "fontSize": 16,
                              "fontWeight": "normal"
                            }
                          ]
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "ryKMx",
                          "name": "p3rest",
                          "fill": "#e5e2e1",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "And it's rolled up in this manner, like here. And then at the end, right here, there's another sticking out, and it means two seals. And that's the way the whole Bible was wrote-in scrolls. And so to break these seals, it opens the mysteries of the book.",
                          "lineHeight": 1.8,
                          "fontFamily": "Noto Serif",
                          "fontSize": 16,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "685gg",
                  "name": "Paragraph 4 - Blue Highlight",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "gap": 16,
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "KEwrs",
                      "name": "p4num",
                      "opacity": 0.5,
                      "fill": "#8E9099",
                      "content": "4",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 12,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "frame",
                      "id": "VNo0v",
                      "name": "P4 Body",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "layout": "vertical",
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "doqYB",
                          "name": "p4pre",
                          "fill": "#e5e2e1",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "Did you get to study in Jeremiah, how he wrote that (many of you taking it down last night)? How them seals were wrote and placed away for keeping until he returned after seventy years of the captivity? He was returned back and claimed his possession. And I certainly would like to state you can't… there is no way to express it all because it is an eternal Word.",
                          "lineHeight": 1.8,
                          "fontFamily": "Noto Serif",
                          "fontSize": 16,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "frame",
                          "id": "qmwFg",
                          "name": "Blue Highlight",
                          "fill": "#60a5fa20",
                          "cornerRadius": 2,
                          "layout": "vertical",
                          "padding": [
                            2,
                            4
                          ],
                          "children": [
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "id": "w94eU",
                              "name": "p4hlText",
                              "fill": "#e5e2e1",
                              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                              "width": 900,
                              "content": "It's an eternal Book. Therefore, we just have to kind of hit the high places.\nAnd today in studying, I have written down many scriptures so you can study it. And also in the tapes will reveal much of it as you study.",
                              "lineHeight": 1.8,
                              "fontFamily": "Noto Serif",
                              "fontSize": 16,
                              "fontWeight": "normal"
                            }
                          ]
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "frame",
                          "id": "6beCP",
                          "name": "Highlight Popover",
