                          "content": "Good evening, friends. It is a great privilege to be back here in the house of the Lord tonight in the service, and still living on the manna from this morning, that our souls were so greatly blessed by his great presence. And now tonight, we are starting on the subject of the Breach Between The Seven Church Ages And The Seven Seals.",
                          "lineHeight": 1.8,
                          "fontFamily": "Noto Serif",
                          "fontSize": 15,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "rectangle",
                      "id": "NI0LQ",
                      "name": "r1sep",
                      "fill": "#2a2a2a",
                      "width": 1,
                      "height": "fill_container"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "frame",
                      "id": "NKKfy",
                      "name": "R1 NO",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "layout": "vertical",
                      "padding": [
                        0,
                        0,
                        0,
                        16
                      ],
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "8lbEl",
                          "name": "r1no",
                          "fill": "#e5e2e1",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "God kveld, venner. Det er et stort privilegium å være tilbake her i Herrens hus i kveld under møtet, og fortsatt leve på mannaen fra i morges, som våre sjeler ble så rikelig velsignet av Hans store nærvær. I kveld starter vi på emnet Brudd Mellom De Syv Menighetsalderene og De Syv Seglene.",
                          "lineHeight": 1.8,
                          "fontFamily": "Noto Serif",
                          "fontSize": 15,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "rectangle",
                  "id": "KqmvR",
                  "name": "Divider",
                  "opacity": 0.4,
                  "fill": "#2a2a2a",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "height": 1
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "Vsi4Z",
                  "name": "Paragraph 2",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "fill": "#1c1b1b",
                  "padding": [
                    24,
                    32
                  ],
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "gBrDj",
                      "name": "r2num",
                      "opacity": 0.5,
                      "fill": "#8E9099",
                      "content": "2",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 12,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "frame",
                      "id": "5wxji",
                      "name": "R2 EN",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "layout": "vertical",
                      "padding": [
                        0,
                        16,
                        0,
                        12
                      ],
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "pLISx",
                          "name": "r2en",
                          "fill": "#e5e2e1",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "So, tonight, while we are kind of getting quietened... I may be just a little lengthy tonight. All the preaching I done in Phoenix I never one time even got hoarse, and for twenty-seven services without getting hoarse. But it is the climate here. It is just bad right here, just a valley.",
                          "lineHeight": 1.8,
                          "fontFamily": "Noto Serif",
                          "fontSize": 15,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "rectangle",
                      "id": "xSvcp",
                      "name": "r2sep",
                      "fill": "#2a2a2a",
                      "width": 1,
                      "height": "fill_container"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "frame",
                      "id": "7UyUh",
                      "name": "R2 NO",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "layout": "vertical",
                      "padding": [
                        0,
                        0,
                        0,
                        16
                      ],
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "tkVNh",
                          "name": "r2no",
                          "fill": "#e5e2e1",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "Så i kveld, mens vi roer oss ned... Jeg kan bli litt langdryg i kveld. All forkynnelsen jeg gjorde i Phoenix fikk meg ikke hes en eneste gang, og det var tjuesju møter uten å bli hes. Men det er klimaet her. Det er rett og slett dårlig rett her, bare en dal.",
                          "lineHeight": 1.8,
                          "fontFamily": "Noto Serif",
                          "fontSize": 15,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "rectangle",
                  "id": "dKr7u",
                  "name": "Divider 2",
                  "opacity": 0.4,
                  "fill": "#2a2a2a",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "height": 1
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "XK7KX",
                  "name": "Paragraph 3",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "fill": "#131313",
                  "padding": [
                    24,
                    32
                  ],
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "fxG5H",
                      "name": "r3num",
                      "opacity": 0.5,
                      "fill": "#8E9099",
                      "content": "3",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 12,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "frame",
                      "id": "w1nLh",
                      "name": "R3 EN",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "layout": "vertical",
                      "padding": [
                        0,
                        16,
                        0,
                        12
                      ],
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "qaa81",
                          "name": "r3en",
                          "fill": "#e5e2e1",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "How many in here has read What Time Is It, Sirs? or has heard it? That has bothered me quite a bit. About a week or ten days ago I was so disturbed. I got up early morning to go up into Sabino Canyon. From the house it is only about thirty minutes drive to the head of the canyon.",
                          "lineHeight": 1.8,
                          "fontFamily": "Noto Serif",
                          "fontSize": 15,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "rectangle",
                      "id": "eLToy",
                      "name": "r3sep",
                      "fill": "#2a2a2a",
                      "width": 1,
                      "height": "fill_container"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "frame",
                      "id": "Dz2Us",
                      "name": "R3 NO",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "layout": "vertical",
                      "padding": [
                        0,
                        0,
                        0,
                        16
                      ],
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "SRTHG",
                          "name": "r3no",
                          "fill": "#e5e2e1",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "Hvor mange her har lest Hva er Klokken, Herrer? eller har hørt den? Det har plaget meg en del. For omtrent en uke eller ti dager siden var jeg så urolig. En tidlig morgen bestemte jeg meg for å dra til Sabino Canyon. Fra huset tar det bare omtrent tretti minutter å kjøre til bunnen av dalen.",
                          "lineHeight": 1.8,
                          "fontFamily": "Noto Serif",
                          "fontSize": 15,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "rectangle",
                  "id": "12VZd",
                  "name": "Divider 3",
                  "opacity": 0.4,
                  "fill": "#2a2a2a",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "height": 1
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "69Zge",
                  "name": "Paragraph 4",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "fill": "#1c1b1b",
                  "padding": [
                    24,
                    32
                  ],
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "xeSNz",
                      "name": "r4num",
                      "opacity": 0.5,
                      "fill": "#8E9099",
                      "content": "4",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 12,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "frame",
                      "id": "LCB8Y",
                      "name": "R4 EN",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "layout": "vertical",
                      "padding": [
                        0,
                        16,
                        0,
                        12
                      ],
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "cCBNo",
                          "name": "r4en",
                          "fill": "#e5e2e1",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "We were at Phoenix just recently where it was twenty something, 28 degrees. They had the swimming pool heated; people swimming. And about forty minutes drive from there, it was forty below zero at Flagstaff. That is the different from the up-currents and the desert.",
                          "lineHeight": 1.8,
                          "fontFamily": "Noto Serif",
                          "fontSize": 15,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "rectangle",
                      "id": "IjGht",
                      "name": "r4sep",
                      "fill": "#2a2a2a",
                      "width": 1,
                      "height": "fill_container"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "frame",
                      "id": "MPJnl",
                      "name": "R4 NO",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "layout": "vertical",
                      "padding": [
                        0,
                        0,
                        0,
                        16
                      ],
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "TWORc",
                          "name": "r4no",
                          "fill": "#e5e2e1",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "Vi var nylig i Phoenix, hvor det var rundt 28 grader. De hadde oppvarmet svømmebasseng; folk badet. Og bare en førti minutters kjøretur derfra, i Flagstaff, var det førti kuldegrader. Dette skyldes forskjellen mellom oppstrømningene og ørkenen.",
                          "lineHeight": 1.8,
                          "fontFamily": "Noto Serif",
                          "fontSize": 15,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
