                          "name": "r4en",
                          "fill": "#e5e2e1",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "We were at Phoenix just recently where it was twenty something, 28 degrees. They had the swimming pool heated; people swimming. And about forty minutes drive from there, it was forty below zero at Flagstaff. That is the different from the up-currents and the desert.",
                          "lineHeight": 1.8,
                          "fontFamily": "Noto Serif",
